column2: SELECT t.AlbumID, SUM (t.UnitPrice) AS totalPrice, COUNT (t.AlbumID) AS numTracks FROM chinook.Track t) SELECT TOP # album.Title, artist.Name, f.totalPrice, f.numTracks FROM f JOIN chinook.Album album ON album.AlbumID = t.AlbumID JOIN chinook.Artist artist ON artist.ArtistID = album.ArtistID ORDER BY totalP DESC
